    "metric_name": "Loan-to-Value Ratio",
    "definition": "Drawn exposure divided by aggregated collateral value with HYBRID sourcing for multi-collateral facilities. Measures credit risk coverage and downside protection. At the facility level, collateral items from collateral_snapshot are SUMmed before dividing into drawn_amount from facility_exposure_snapshot. Higher tiers use exposure-weighted averages.",
